    "description": "Tata CLiQ Capital India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Bengaluru operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Tata CLiQ Capital India:\nTata CLiQ Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata CLiQ Capital India!",
